description:
Thought I'd try to make a GAMING VIDEO [GOD FORBID :O :O :O]  Anyway, I finally got the means of recording gameplay footage, and I have always wanted to to make a TF2 video. If this gets a positive reaction, I'll try to make more! 

YES, I AM STILL MAKING YTPS.
